title: Episode 54 t. Premium Pete and Miss Lissa
itunes:title: Episode 54 t. Premium Pete and Miss Lissa
description:
Premium Pete and Miss Lissa from the "Premium Pete Show" cross-pollinated with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire on "Lip Service" to discuss dealing with difficult baby mamas, the worst lie they ever told, and dating someone with a disability. Things get heated toward the end, so check it out and see if you think Premium Pete was being inappropriate
